All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<Step>, Collection<Step>, Set<Step>
public class StepSet extends HashSet<Step>
A StepSet is a HashSet of Steps that can be saved in an XMLControl.

Douglas Brown
